<item>
            <title>[OPENJPA-340] @UniqueConstraint and corresponding XML ignored</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-340</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;OpenJPA ignores @UniqueConstraint annotations (and the corresponding XML declaration) when generating database schemas. This should be rectified.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A workaround is to set the -ignoreErrors flag to true when running mappingtool, which will let schema creation continue despite the error.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12377008">OPENJPA-340</key>
            <summary>@UniqueConstraint and corresponding XML ignored</summary>
